name: Alejandra Silva
summary: Alejandra Silva is a 29-year-old woman who identifies herself under the pronouns "She/Her/Hers" and is of Hispanic/Latino ethnicity. She grew up in Miami, Florida, and currently lives in Los Angeles, California while working as a Community Outreach Specialist in the non-profit sector. She is a graduate from the University of California and is intellectually stimulated by reading. She is fluent in English, Spanish, and French and enjoys travelling, finger painting, hiking, and cooking. Alejandra is spiritually inclined and leans towards liberal politics. Her essential values include compassion, justice, art, nature, and education. A dog and cat lover, she sometimes likes to have a drink but stays away from smoking. She is actively involved in exercise and sport and her MBTI personality type is ENFP. Alejandra hopes to find a life partner who is a non-smoker, keeps active, and is interested in having children in the future.
